eading, writing, checking existence, deleting files, and creating directories—all delegating to the underlying `IFileSystem` interface.","outputTokens":776,"requestId":"5C2B:96AFF:31B0A9:3DD84E:69F5590C"},"id":"4b00796f-59bf-4b0d-a636-5743b709ebb6","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:53:33.492Z","parentId":"beef151d-ca9d-4629-a2fb-0330f08f7adf"}
